        <!-- Marketing and User Experience Section -->
        <section class="marketing-section">
            <div class="marketing-content">
                <h2>Marketing Strategies and User Experience</h2>
                <p>
                    The plan to market the application included implementing SEO and digital marketing strategies to attract users interested in technology and leisure. The idea was to create optimized ads on social media, along with exclusive promotions for early app downloaders. In addition, close collaboration with affiliated venues was planned to ensure a smooth user experience, with attractive offers that incentivized app usage.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The interface is designed to be intuitive, offering a smooth experience for both residents and tourists.
                    Users can navigate through bar promotions, order taxis, or check bus schedules in seconds.
                </p>
