        <!-- Business Intent and Growth Plan Section -->
        <section>
            <h2>Business Intent and Growth Plan</h2>
            <p>
                The idea behind Baretos Baratos is not only to provide a useful application for users,
                but also to become a profitable platform for bars and restaurants in Zaragoza.
                As the user base grows, the intention is to integrate more services and collaborations with venues across the city.
            </p>
            <p>
                In the future, there are plans to expand to other cities, replicating the Zaragoza model in other urban centers with a
                diverse nightlife and social offering.
            </p>
        </section>
